<A>__{one last, bloody, violent bit of play then, mercifully, the final whistle blows. final score: lions 32 springboks 15. the lions celebrate. the springboks head off the field, heads down, shoulders bowed in defeat none more bitterly disappointed or bloodier than francois pienaar. in the stands, the unheard of happens the springboks are booed by their own fans. not by everybody, but by enough. we stay with the `boks as they trudge across the field, then clatter along the concrete tunnel to their dressing room.}
